    	   level(F)
       Example
           R = QQ[x,y]
     	   M = R^1/ideal(x,y)
    	   level(M)
   Caveat
       Text
       	   Over singular rings, level only returns correct answers wrt perfect complexes
   SeeAlso
       ghost
